de.charite.compbio.jannovar.reference

Interface TranscriptSupportLevels


  • public interface TranscriptSupportLevels
    Container for constants of transcript support levels. In the case that the transcript support level is not available, 6 is used as a substitute for transcripts that are marked as primary in UCSC, 7 for the longest transcript (in absence of both level and UCSC primary marking), and 8 for transcripts that fall neither into pseudo-level 6 and 7. A value of -1 is used for N/A.
    Author:
    Manuel Holtgrewe
    See Also:
    http://www.ensembl.org/Help/Glossary?id=492
